data.description: Better than new construction! 3bed, 2 bath home nestled along the back end of Rose Rock Estates Addition. Super clean and move in ready! Bright and spacious living/dining spaces. Masterbed ensuite is at the back of the house and has a huge master closet/bathroom with a soaking tub/separate shower. Spare bedrooms are in front of the house with a hall bathroom. Close to OU Campus, Lloyd Noble Center, and retail shopping. Big backyard situated perfectly for entertaining.
